<item>
            <title>[LU-16609] top_trans_create() can oom due to the gfp flags</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16609</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;top_trans_create() requests __GFP_IO memory allocation, &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
which does not allow direct reclaim. However, if the &lt;br/&gt;
memory shortage is temporary, direct reclaim is reasonable. &lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;GFP_NOFS is __GFP_IO with some additional reclaim bits.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="74903">LU-16609</key>
            <summary>top_trans_create() can oom due to the gfp flags</summary>
