                            <comment id="462017" author="eaujames" created="Tue, 1 Jul 2025 06:45:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The CEA hit this issue during benchmark (with mdtest). I backported the patch for 2.15.&lt;br/&gt;
We use &quot;&lt;em&gt;watermark_scale_factor&lt;/em&gt;&quot; to mitigate this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="461930" author="gerrit" created="Mon, 30 Jun 2025 21:18:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;Etienne AUJAMES &amp;lt;eaujames@ddn.com&amp;gt;&quot; uploaded a new patch: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/59989&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/59989&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
